{"type": "article", "id": 5820, "title": "ATH-R70x 耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-03T07:36:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234018fiAmHMgxweBaEjdh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日前，日本电子音像公司铁三角推出了一款专业级开放式监听耳机 ATH-R70x，配有独特的双边式可更换导线，不管连接方式如何，都能自动保持适当的立体声左右定位。ATH-R70x 配有特别设计的驱动器和铝质金属的蜂窝网外罩。这款耳机使用了新型的支撑系统，自身重量仅仅有 210 克，即便是长时间戴着，也不会产生不适的体验，保持良好的配戴感。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234016Veagn5B4UkpyJOE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340170a1ypcNeIWzCVQ5A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.903125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340177XvUDGBdhqE85YoH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}